                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9498" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">PJMT-0156</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1451 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">瓯江山水工程的组织管理创新：两山理论在外籍学者中的传播</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Organization management innovation of Oujiang Landscape Project: Dissemination of the Two Mountains Theory among foreign scholars</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘小峰，胡华屹，王硕，梁雅莉，张利民，王大哲</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">丽水市自然资源和规划局</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">公共管理和社会组织</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山水工程；项目组织管理；数字化监管；协同治理理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Landscape engineering; Project organization management; Digital regulation; Cooperative governance theory</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例基于国际视野描述了瓯江山水工程组织架构、组织协同和组织监管等管理创新举措，深入分析了项目组织管理和协同治理理论在工程中的应用与实践。通过“两山理论”的视角，揭示了瓯江山水工程取得成功的关键因素，为全球生态修复难题提供了具有中国特色的解决方案。本案例旨在引导学生站在国际视角思考和理解瓯江山水工程项目组织管理创新的制度背景和外在表现，并进一步厘清山水工程组织管理模式的适应性、探索性和先进性。本案例展示了中国特有的领导小组和工作专班组织坚持“绿水青山就是金山银山”，在多重任务多元目标下突破困难与挑战下大力践行山水林田湖草生命共同体理念的行动与担当。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all"> Based on an international perspective, this case describes the management innovation measures such as the organizational structure, organizational coordination and organizational supervision of the Oujiang River landscape project. We analyzes the application and practice of project organization management and collaborative governance theory in engineering. Through the perspective of the &quot;two mountains theory&quot;, the key factors for the success of the Oujiang River landscape project are revealed.This provides a solution with Chinese characteristics to the global ecological restoration problem.This case aims to guide students to think and understand the institutional background and external manifestations of Oujiang landscape engineering organization and management innovation from an international perspective, and further clarify the adaptability, exploration and advancement of the landscape engineering organization and management model. This case shows the actions and responsibilities of China&#39;s unique leading group and working group organization, which adhere to the &quot;clear waters and green mountains are gold hills and silver mountains&quot;, and vigorously implement the concept of life community of mountains, forests, fields, lakes and grasses under multiple tasks and multiple goals.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《项目管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">项目组织管理；综合集成管理；领导小组与工作专班；项目组织结构；协同治理理论；项目监督管理；数字化监管；两山理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-03</td>
                            </tr>
